extending from the cieling that Skulletron could do the gymanstic stuff on in 
the entire Cybertronian Fire, save the engine room.

Again, you have no way of knowing this, and you're just trying to save your 
character.  But people, please stop making crap up like laundry chutes.  For 
the laundry chute thing, Cybertronians don't use clothing!  

Also, if Skulletron jumped up towards the cieling, the autogun blasts could 
reach him faster.  So I'm gonna let you repost that, since you had no idea 
the bridge lacked pipes fromt he cieling)
